Youngstown.WYTV-DT2: WYTV-DT2 is a digital subchannel of ABC affiliate WYTV for the Mahoning Valley of Northeastern Ohio and Northwestern Pennsylvania. owned by Vaughan Media, but operated through a shared services agreement (SSA) and a joint sales agreement (JSA) by Nexstar Media Group. It is affiliated with MyNetworkTV. It broadcasts in standard definition on 33.2.
